      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until golden and crispy</p><p>Once crispy, transfer the<strong> bacon</strong> to kitchen paper and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
