          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\"> [350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1677587785781-x200.jpg",
