      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the vegetables are cooking, add your <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked spaghetti</strong> and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
