    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> to a large bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and mix to combine</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> dressed salad</strong></p><p>Break the <strong>crispy bacon</strong> into small pieces</p>",
