    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> veg-packed tomato spaghetti</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>crispy bacon pieces</strong> over the spaghetti and serve the <strong>dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
